data.description: This Bates-Hendricks charmer is exactly where you want to be. Want a new build without the wait?! Here it is! Featuring 3 large bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a beautiful 2 tier deck perfect for entertaining that leads you to your spacious BRAND NEW 2 car garage. At 1900 sq ft, this contemporary style home is move in ready with open concept, beautiful kitchen with custom countertops, large island and stainless steel appliances. Did I mention the option of a master on the main and upstairs? This home is BRAND NEW & READY FOR YOU.
